    <h1>Entity SEO and Why It Matters for AI Search</h1>

    <blockquote>
      <p><strong>Entity SEO</strong> is the practice of making it easier for search engines and AI systems to understand who you are, what you do, what topics you belong to, and why your brand should be trusted as a source or recommendation.</p>
    </blockquote>

    <p>Traditional SEO often over-focuses on pages and keywords. AI search adds another layer: can the system understand the brand behind the page?</p>

    <p>That matters because AI tools do not only retrieve documents. They also infer relationships. They connect brands to categories, experts to topics, and services to problems. If those signals are weak, your content can still rank while your brand stays forgettable.</p>

